| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0349 — Recovery Inhibition (darkvault)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 36c1db4c-5f5f-5744-a3f7-9189a6649dd2"
